🦆 CONTEXT
"Duck Master" is a casual game about circling target ducks within a limit time. With a simple yet dynamic interaction, players long press the mouse to scale the capture circle, releasing it with a precise timing to catch their fluffy feathered friends. Each circling will only match one goal. Dive into our game filled with delightful music, dynamic animation, and adorable ducks, and challenge yourself through the quests to become a Duck Master!

🎮 CONTROLS                                  🐣 GAMEPLAY


